{
  "stem": "717.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You will see it later when you interview Regina from Regina at the cemetery when she was I think five years old.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we have a photo of Sylvia when she was five years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it's like one face.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Dinah, she's called after my mother, is the spitting image of my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now I don't remember anymore, but when she was born, when she grew up, I could see my mother in her.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the time came for us to leave, we were a little hesitant.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, 15 years in Australia, you're established.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What kind of work did you do there?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Australia in the fur trade.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I managed a store.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Five years, I worked on one job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first job that I had in a big firm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, no, 10 years I worked for [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Davis ?] Brothers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the last five years I worked for a guy, he wanted me very much.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had a small store and a small factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wanted me to manage the store and the factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to work for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was better paying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was closer to the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we needed more money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The family grew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I worked there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I did some private work also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I work very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think this probably pushed me to make the decision to leave.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked that job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very responsible because I was responsible for the workers, for everything, for the-- the work to be finished on time, and I couldn't give up the theater, rehearsals.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the beginning, two rehearsals a week, one rehearsal a week, near the end, every day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The last play we did in 1964 it was Sholem Aleichem's And I play the lead.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
